text: Rudrasen Chaudhary is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Lok Sabha, the lower house of the Parliament of India as a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. ==References== ==External links== * Official biographical sketch in Parliament of India website Category:1930 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Lok Sabha members from Uttar Pradesh Category:6th Lok Sabha members Category:9th Lok Sabha members Category:10th Lok Sabha members Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians from Uttar Pradesh Category:Janata Party politicians Category:Bharatiya Lok Dal politicians
